<HEAD>Eighteen Killed After Boats Capsize Off Bangladesh</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DHAKA, Bangladesh (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   At least 18 fishermen drowned after
their boats capsized in the Bay of Bengal off the southern port of
